One <termsem="SO:0000704"> gene </term> , RIKEN <termsem="SO:0000756"> cDNA </term> 4933409K07 ( Figure 1 , <termsem="SO:0000704"> gene </term> G47 ) , was found to be up-regulated on microarray at all four timepoints examined .
